    <div class="footer-top">
      <div class="footer-brand">
        <div class="wordmark">
          <svg class="leaf" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M12 22V8" stroke="#6FC23A" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round"></path>
            <path d="M12 9C12 5 8.5 2.5 4.5 2.5 4.5 7 7.5 9.5 12 9Z" fill="#6FC23A"></path>
            <path d="M12 11c0-3 3-5 6.5-5 0 3.6-2.8 5.6-6.5 5Z" fill="#3A5BE0"></path>
          </svg>
          <span class="wm-text">YIMEI</span>
        </div>
        <p>Engineering treatment flows that turn industrial waste into reusable water.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-col">
        <h4>Explore</h4>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
          <li><a href="/products">Products</a></li>
          <li><a href="/events">Events</a></li>
          <li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-col">
